 aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zyj1665702550619.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zyj1665702550619.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zyj1665702550619.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zyj1665702550619\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Component Field\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Component Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Component Entity.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d94973e1_d94974e1_d94975e1\">A Component Field that is created using a Modeled Field is\n      a <dfn class=\"term\">derived field</dfn> and inherits from the Modeled Field.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__section_glj_mgr_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d114977e57\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__image_uwt_pgr_lwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component_field.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fld</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lym1665702585074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lym1665702585074.html\" title=\"A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior.\">Field</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aam1665702585156.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aam1665702585156.html\" title=\"A Derived Component Field references a Modeled Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers.\">Derived Component Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"blb1665703026348.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/blb1665703026348.html\" title=\"A non-derived field is a Component Field that has been created from a template, not a Modeled Field. It is always a none-database field, even if its parent is a derived entity.\">Non-Derived Field</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generates:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zyj1665702550619__table_d10511e1_d10512e1_d10513e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>/fld:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__section_ry5_tgr_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d114977e308\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d94982e1_d94983e1_d94984e1\">Component Field specializes Development Object and Field\n        in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__ul_bdx_5gr_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37313e1_d37314e1_d37315e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d94985e1_d94986e1_d94987e1\">It has a Component Entity as parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37316e1_d37317e1_d37318e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d94988e1_d94989e1_d94990e1\">It defines a data field, control, or constant\n            data.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37319e1_d37320e1_d37321e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d94991e1_d94992e1_d94993e1\">It has a widget type and widget properties.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__section_hzq_vgr_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d114977e338\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d94997e1_d94998e1_d94999e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__ul_uns_wgr_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37322e1_d37323e1_d37324e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37325e1_d37326e1_d37327e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37328e1_d37329e1_d37330e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37331e1_d37332e1_d37333e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37334e1_d37335e1_d37336e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d95000e1_d95001e1_d95002e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__ul_f4s_wgr_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37337e1_d37338e1_d37339e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jtg1665702585772.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtg1665702585772.html\" title=\"This property indicates whether the current object inherits from a modeled object. Boolean read-only.\">Inherits</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37340e1_d37341e1_d37342e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tgz1665702585851.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tgz1665702585851.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the development object from which the current object inherits. Depending on the context, it may be read-only or editable.\">Inherits From</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37343e1_d37344e1_d37345e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"puj1665702585966.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/puj1665702585966.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the entity or field is generic. Applicable only in modeled components.\">Is Generic</a> (only in modeled components)</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37346e1_d37347e1_d37348e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sdh1665702586086.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sdh1665702586086.html\" title=\"This property indicates whether the entity or field is bound to a generic entity or field in a modeled component. Boolean read-only.\">Is Bound</a> (only in derived components)</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37349e1_d37350e1_d37351e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ljd1665702586171.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ljd1665702586171.html\" title=\"This property defines the name of the generic entity or field in a modeled component to which the current object is bound.\">Bound To</a> (only in derived components)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d95003e1_d95004e1_d95005e1\">Data I/O Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__ul_p4s_wgr_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37352e1_d37353e1_d37354e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aww1665702586248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aww1665702586248.html\" title=\"Uniface data type to use for this field, variable, or parameter. The default value is S (String).\">Data Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37355e1_d37356e1_d37357e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pta1665702586322.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pta1665702586322.html\" title=\"Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter.\">Is External</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37358e1_d37359e1_d37360e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iri1665702586413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iri1665702586413.html\" title=\"Determines whether the field contents are same for all occurrences of the entity.\">Is Static</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37361e1_d37362e1_d37363e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oji1665702586488.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oji1665702586488.html\" title=\"Determines whether the field is a control field in a form component, meaning that it can be selected with the mouse but not get focus. This affects validation behavior.\">Is Control</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37364e1_d37365e1_d37366e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"enu1665702584272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enu1665702584272.html\" title=\"This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database.\">Database Interface (Entities)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37367e1_d37368e1_d37369e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zlt1665702557043.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlt1665702557043.html\" title=\"The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37370e1_d37371e1_d37372e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpv1665702557117.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpv1665702557117.html\" title=\"Property that specifies how the field's data is formatted for display. The value can be a comma-separated list of shorthand codes, or a reference to a modeled field layout.\">Field Layout</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37373e1_d37374e1_d37375e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wen1665702586573.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wen1665702586573.html\" title=\"Value that should be displayed in this field at runtime; can be a default for the user or the actual field value.\">Initial Value</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d95006e1_d95007e1_d95008e1\">Presentation properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__ul_fps_wgr_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37376e1_d37377e1_d37378e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nnt1665702586853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nnt1665702586853.html\" title=\"Name of the pop-up menu object to display when the user clicks the mouse button in this component, entity, or field.\">Pop-up Menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37379e1_d37380e1_d37381e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wcj1665702586648.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcj1665702586648.html\" title=\"Type of widget to use for this entity or field in Form (and Report) components.\">FRM Widget Type (Field)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d95009e1_d95010e1_d95011e1\">Area Frames presentation properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__ul_jps_wgr_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37382e1_d37383e1_d37384e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vsj1665703026566.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vsj1665703026566.html\" title=\"This property specifies a user-defined logical widget that can be used to style the area frame.\">Widget Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37385e1_d37386e1_d37387e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37388e1_d37389e1_d37390e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37391e1_d37392e1_d37393e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37394e1_d37395e1_d37396e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37397e1_d37398e1_d37399e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mok1665702703254.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mok1665702703254.html\" title=\"The number of times the entity or area frame is repeated horizontally in a Form or Report. The minimum (and default) is 1.\">Horizontal Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37400e1_d37401e1_d37402e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fmf1665702703323.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fmf1665702703323.html\" title=\"The number of times the entity or area frame is repeated vertically in a Form or Report. The minimum (and default) is 1.\">Vertical Repetition</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37403e1_d37404e1_d37405e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gmd1665702587249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmd1665702587249.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a border is displayed around the area frame, entity or occurrence frame, or field. It is set from the context menu in the form canvas.\">Border</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37406e1_d37407e1_d37408e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d95012e1_d95013e1_d95014e1\">Print Frames presentation properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__ul_aqs_wgr_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37409e1_d37410e1_d37411e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37412e1_d37413e1_d37414e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37415e1_d37416e1_d37417e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37418e1_d37419e1_d37420e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37421e1_d37422e1_d37423e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gmd1665702587249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmd1665702587249.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a border is displayed around the area frame, entity or occurrence frame, or field. It is set from the context menu in the form canvas.\">Border</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__li_d37424e1_d37425e1_d37426e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zyj1665702550619__p_d95015e1_d95016e1_d95017e1\">Object frame properties are defined in the Define Frames\n        worksheet.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617519\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617519\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Component Field Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Component Field A Component Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Component Entity. A Component Field that is created using a Modeled Field is a derived field and inherits from the Modeled Field. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: fld Main Development Object? No Part of: Component Entity Contains: Value, Property , Code Container Generalization: Field Specializations: — Derived Component Field , Non-Derived Field Compilation output: — Generates: — URI format: cpt: ComponentName /ent: EntityName /fld: FieldName Specialization Component Field specializes Development Object and Field in the following ways: It has a Component Entity as parent. It defines a data field, control, or constant data. It has a widget type and widget properties. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Configuration Properties: Inherits Inherits From Is Generic (only in modeled components) Is Bound (only in derived components) Bound To (only in derived components) Data I/O Properties: Data Type Is External Is Static Is Control Database Interface (Entities) Field Syntax Field Layout Initial Value Presentation properties: Pop-up Menu FRM Widget Type (Field) Area Frames presentation properties: Widget Type Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Horizontal Repetition Vertical Repetition Border Index Color Print Frames presentation properties: Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Border Index Color Object frame properties are defined in the Define Frames worksheet. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}